# NIX PATH-INFO
Nixpkgs: nixpkgs.nix
Source: https://github.com/NixOS/nix
Description: Query information about store paths.
Version: nix --version

## Commands

### Basics
- nix path-info -h /nix/store/... : Show size of a store path.

### Essentials
- nix path-info -Sh nixpkgs#htop: Show the total size including dependencies (Closure).

### Intermediaries
- nix path-info --json nixpkgs#hello: Get detailed path info in JSON.

### Advanceds
- nix path-info --closure-size -h nixpkgs#python3: Check disk space impact.

## Tips
- Use -S for cumulative size (Closure) and -h for human-readable output.

